@startuml
title Plane State Transition Diagram

[*] --> Order

state Order
state Arrival
state Preparation
state Operations
state Maintenance
state OutOfService
state Removed

Order --> Arrival : delivered

Arrival --> Preparation : arrive

Preparation --> Operations : assign to operations
Preparation --> Maintenance : assign to maintenance

Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights

Maintenance --> Preparation : serviced and ready

Operations --> [*] : taken out of service

Operations --> Removed : permanently withdrawn

Maintenance --> [*] : serviced and ready

OutOfService --> [*] : plane becomes available

Removed --> [*] : plane is no longer in service

@enduml
